{"hb4966a07g1b01g4a3dgb889gc0cd3320a7c2": ["Good morning! And it truly is, isn't it? A very, very good morning.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "29b76140-650a-50a2-5496-ea495c196776"], "h12602f0cg1ecdg410dgbc11gd6e324a7f1f8": ["There's a glow about you, no doubt about me too. We feel... startlingly well.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "779cd956-0082-53f1-aaab-f8e21359a61b"], "hcbbedf58g809cg4b2cg8e7agd281323309ba": ["And yet there's a certain look in your eyes. The far off distance of a haunting.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "e23b8437-6349-78bd-0148-f0c1e47d63ee"], "hf72de82dg3ffdg4715g85d0ge5e00ca0ee7c": ["What I saw surpassed the vivid. The voice was too true, the touch too tantalising. I can tell you felt the same.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "579271b3-01ed-64a7-714c-bd4561248006"], "h094a2225g3e26g4437gac7age016611600b3": ["It was an expert, this apparition. First the seduction, then the spurning, then that teasing souvenir.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "4e250833-cb98-2ba5-0716-8c73cf6b958a"], "h3c036c55ge146g4450g8be7g5cba431945c4": ["'You're not ready. I will return when you are.' That's what I was promised.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "217438c5-1fcc-d146-d96f-8f507e54acf5"], "h82d6dad9gfb32g4aceg9c82g00d6113fbf01": ["We have some restless nights ahead of us.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "5c3b5a5a-fa57-1d50-f50f-9b7f98f60778"], "h659515d1g4e2dg4a18g812fgc4a14d878f04": ["There's a glow about you, about everyone here. We all feel... startlingly well.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "b6aa8d9e-7c1c-8041-2191-0793f3767cd6"], "hf68618e1g2268g4de1g84c4g0c8ce4cca2ff": ["And yet there's a certain look in people's eyes. The far off distance of a haunting.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "5b0611c7-1e41-ce7d-2efa-fdfdeaf42fd7"], "h8d25cf9ag1ad2g415cg9019gb7ff21442bb2": ["The night brings council, or so the saying goes, but last night had quite a bit more in store, wouldn't you agree?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "5b2472e2-b095-bf29-abd1-4147a33e3c38"], "h670a6594g9dbbg4a8cg8e50g70419bd3d649": ["Which begs yet another question: did you too have such puzzling dreams?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "d221164b-ae10-7eb8-7455-5fafc52404bb"], "h42bc21b5ga95dg425dg9d1ag55751ef05097": ["Actually, my dreams were quite delightful.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "ae12e7fa-63bf-d731-8b1d-dcd5b7cf5e8b"], "h1898bed0ge382g434cgbbf4g5bebf8ce14c1": ["Surely not the only adjective that springs to mind.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "4ab0a6bf-8d97-39ac-ba0f-70b0027bce9e"], "hb7f6fd32gb0eag499dga385g696c46e123d1": ["<i>You nod in silence.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "995c5221-bd01-fbc9-198a-3ab94338b7c9"], "h249c1b62gad86g42abgb102ge4a09058cb21": ["Same here. Perhaps. The jury's still out.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "4c513aa8-8b53-12e4-e1bc-4648c99ba437"], "hc5093bbbg839cg4cc8gadd7g5b02437c6216": ["Mind your own business, Gale.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "c909da69-b292-ab4f-d6c2-807f98bc79ee"], "h94297a66g24afg4eb7gb05dg7b519be6e844": ["Not a morning person, I see. But those eyes of yours speak volumes.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "dc5b43ad-0c01-82e7-5cd8-0a9de8aeb46e"], "h657f9cd5g89e2g42f1gb736gc1be05999651": ["Do you feel as chipper as I do?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "439c850a-a0b0-a760-7e60-ac3a3843435a"], "ha1ac30c9g7042g4069ga84ag1d5adcecf9fd": ["How's that for feeling better?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "415ca216-7fc1-ac21-2e7c-0b4e511c3f76"], "h6b2347a4g1628g4e1cga791gaf71b98eed57": ["I see I'm not the only one who woke with newfelt powers.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "ad03926f-884d-2495-f4a5-bb9b025f7ab9"], "h52cad230ge763g44f9g9771g3fbad47f3019": ["Hardly.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "c813e5e1-6b4c-699b-3607-8910e281d73f"], "hc2f5c8a8g704cg4f8fga97fg92d8f5e61c2f": ["Actually, my dreams were quite delightful.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "e01d6831-2a77-cae3-6863-4c958f936891"], "h80dbd196g51a7g4c07gadc2gbaf38f875d6d": ["Sought out in the night by... what? An illusion, or a promise?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "47e756aa-bccb-463e-6c9c-f30ae61f93ab"], "h5c5ae59bg0ac1g4ac5g8afagd204cf6caf46": ["I don't see the distinction.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "443a54a5-b8e6-fa1d-7b62-083db8625058"], "h0ecc5fb0ge724g416agb303g35e9cb85a2f7": ["An illusion is only a lie, but a promise is a truth that may yet come to pass.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "c9f33706-4301-4a93-4ead-ca0250669ce6"], "h1eb17288gecd5g4256ga25bga333b0a37468": ["As for the lure of the touch, the kiss, the everything...", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "91424e02-52fb-8e1e-9e1b-b766758a9f6f"], "h7eed79e9g5f8ag4ac0g9c3bgdf560e8e8cf5": ["Did you relent or resist?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "9580c15b-6e2b-91ca-316c-7f2c0235e0b5"], "h1715a436g7774g4ae5g90dag0065c036ba51": ["I relented.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "98384cff-f867-a9ce-758e-c504dcca46b9"], "h86d7c867g8539g4d79gba57g18a505516b0c": ["It felt impossible not to. I did as well.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "e6511f2f-f123-3e1b-ecc4-67e7b6e76133"], "h11409bdfg0c7ag4eabgab01gcf2c5b584c0f": ["<i>Lie and say you relented.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "2eeba1ba-8cf1-347f-9054-8e09fc7ea03c"], "hf9984040g6b9cg4e6eg9766g770e103738de": ["I resisted.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "4c8acffb-ca29-1eaa-1eb8-fb4b6b38cfb0"], "h1c8365f2gc6f1g49f9g8c6fgef78aa6be7bb": ["Then you're stronger than me.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "f2796a96-d0c2-b61f-c726-28ba69c618d4"], "he2e2c8c2gd096g4e29gbdfcge716fe29f104": ["<i>Lie and say you resisted.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "8a713601-6842-34b0-65fd-de7151697b7c"], "h554c9efcg8517g4512gaa60ga99aaa9d9e30": ["Neither: I remained silent.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "2c576f4e-748e-e690-591f-84d518a22d6d"], "h5c35d279gb501g4597gb270g3e0e063879f4": ["I could not. I relented. It felt impossible not to.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "d1ae0668-a503-5668-d4c9-e31cf8130c55"], "hcec5766ege212g4b06g948ag3a3399e15684": ["<i>Lie and say you remained silent.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "608e0225-3b00-a1ea-ffa0-7c5c9d0292e4"], "h7e9bbc8ag13feg476eg9df4g97782a919660": ["How about you tell me what you did?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "679c686d-dabc-4108-4a52-f5b93e7d01a2"], "hcf75809bg8792g467fg8f22gb1fefb1f29b7": ["I relented. It felt impossible not to.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "0ed3538b-9f23-f35c-c6a3-878deb61ef1f"], "hb5928e5egd05fg4601g8b00gfbaa294c1bef": ["The kiss, you say. Now I know why you're so chipper.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "26687ad7-b06f-051c-c64a-e4b5a08ca42e"], "h31322d13gf3b3g47adgb910ged800be6e27e": ["The dream wasn't just about power, it was also about desire. But that doesn't answer my question:", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "c054e753-a955-ddc8-3bb9-4593d1537c1f"], "h0a55032dg6e28g4f26g970cg78f6cd4ad47f": ["It felt more like being prey cornered by a predator.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "2da105ac-a78d-91ea-557a-5e887b891725"], "hccded7ecg5376g44aeg92c9gf8b664bc7994": ["And you consider that to be delightful?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "06ee5739-dd2b-d8cf-821a-2bdf114bd69f"], "h285364ccg04f8g40fegb99eg31a8d22a27a6": ["Let's agree that at the very least there was the <i>lure</i> of a promise.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "a5949a7d-54a9-2cea-3b97-dd3ace5aa9c3"], "h223f2252g946ag4482g853fg96b7af73130c": ["The touch, the kiss, the everything...", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "b25fa1d6-324e-1900-9d4f-0782ce02ff5d"], "h730d4ca1g8a03g48c2gb1b0gd29bd799ae9e": ["All too apt an analogy.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "5055cbac-831c-14c9-feaa-bc3c925ad0ba"], "ha851e019g9a40g4cf7gbe63g0ea1d544bde1": ["It was more than a promise: these powers are real.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "e06e7905-1b54-1de4-6338-1cdb9fa6110d"], "hf8b809f5g3982g48efga9ccg17c42f235393": ["You have me there.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "70387f14-47ca-8ab8-a50b-6ccfef011fb7"], "ha44594ffgce5bg46c9gaff9g4707636a71fa": ["<i>You nod in silence.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "59d18c7c-7d33-ebe0-45de-66f01b421136"], "h7ea491afg4c52g4f5dga487g842ee8ce3e48": ["Mind your own business, Gale.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "689e7b49-9b73-d928-cb4e-1e22735737f4"], "ha68f5f39g06a5g4144g842eg4b64f7f53bf2": ["It's remarkable how much better I feel after feeling so sick earlier.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "d503e0c5-0844-5da5-af3c-a98d44f4ba67"], "h36f6b8d0g3973g4126gb070gfd9d1b75d6d8": ["Remarkable - or perhaps we should call it suspicious.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "a31d81ae-37e8-5181-0daf-ffad4dd99bd9"], "h4173b581g4bedg4b25ga308gf9880cdf2ba2": ["Those are a lot of questions so early in the morning.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "81be8b7d-c531-4469-0ff0-42b011dbe19d"], "h6fa99b99g443ag4ba1gaeddg1d00c1fd2795": ["That's because there's so much to ask.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "0c3f2bd3-e40e-47f1-7f33-f7766dfde6e2"], "hdd7f99f1g64bag4699g9feagf413da768e36": ["Why don't we just skip to the part where we have some breakfast?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "b231ac47-917b-15d4-25e1-65565d80f6de"], "h83d79072g5249g43b9gb869gac9a61cd2d5f": ["Let's settle another appetite first.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_WRD_Gale.html", "bbb729ed-511f-1ca4-39f8-04625ca96ee9"]}